    <node id="STREAMS">
      <data key="d0">CONCEPT</data>
      <data key="d1">Streams refer to the flow of data or information, possibly related to customer activity or transactions, and have unique identifiers, customer IDs, content IDs, and other attributes&gt;
Streams refer to the flow of data or information, possibly related to content streaming or viewer activity}</data>
